PORT=Port number of the server. (optional)
PROXY=Proxies for requests (optional) (e.g. ["https://proxy1.com", "https://proxy2.com"])
OUTBOUND_PROXIES=Comma-separated or JSON array proxy list for outbound requests (optional)
JUSTANIME_PROXY=Proxy used exclusively for JustAnime requests (optional) (e.g. http://host:port) — useful for local dev
ENABLE_TOR_PROXY=Enable Tor SOCKS proxy fallback (optional) (true/false)
TOR_PROXY_URL=Tor SOCKS URL (optional) (default: socks5h://127.0.0.1:9050)
REDIS_HOST=Redis host (optional)
REDIS_PORT=Redis port (optional)
REDIS_TTL=Redis cache timeout (seconds) (optional)
REDIS_PASSWORD=Redis password (optional)
TMDB_KEY=TMDB access token auth (optional)
YOUTUBE_API_KEY=YouTube Data API v3 key for trailer fetching (optional)
NODE_ENV=Environment (optional) (DEMO or PROD)
NETMIRROR_BASE_URL=NetMirror base URL (optional) (default: https://net20.cc)
NETMIRROR_OTT=NetMirror OTT code (optional) (default: nf)
NETMIRROR_T_HASH_T=NetMirror t_hash_t token (required for netmirror)
